snippet.title: Employee of The Month - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
An atmospheric retro inspired survival horror game. Enjoy the late shift at 'The Month' in an abstract and unsettling night of terror, spooks and convenience.

Coming soon to Steam and Itch.io. Demo currently available on Itch.io

Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1957230/Employee_of_The_Month/

Itch.io : https://projecktskeleton.itch.io/employee-of-the-month
